Deprecated API

Contents

  • Interfaces
  • Methods
  • Interfaces 
    Interface Description
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.HasElements
    No longer necessary. Use Iterable<HTMLElement> instead.
  • Methods 
    Method Description
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.builder.ElementBuilder.asElement()
    In order to cleanup the API and to avoid multiple methods which do (or return) the same thing, builders won't implement IsElement<E> in the next major version. Please use ElementBuilder.get() instead. A builder is a builder and not an element.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.builder.ElementBuilder.element()
    In order to cleanup the API and to avoid multiple methods which do (or return) the same thing, builders won't implement IsElement<E> in the next major version. Please use ElementBuilder.get() instead. A builder is a builder and not an element.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.builder.ElementsBuilder.addAll​(HasElements)
    Please use ElementsBuilder.addAll(Iterable) instead.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.builder.ElementsBuilder.asElements()
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.builder.HtmlContent.addAll​(HasElements)
    Please use HtmlContent.addAll(Iterable) instead.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.Elements.createDocumentUniqueId()
    Replaced by Elements.uniqueId()
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.Elements.elements()
    Renamed to avoid confusion with Elements.elements(JsArrayLike). Please use Elements.collect() instead.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.HasElements.asElements()
    Please use methods from Iterable instead.
    org.jboss.gwt.elemento.core.LazyElement.asElement()
    Please use LazyElement.element() instead.
